  "notes": [
    "This pilot study investigated the prevalence and clinical implications of reversible tactile hypoesthesia in patients with myofascial trigger points.",
    "The study found that 58.7% of patients showed reduction in hypoesthetic areas with trigger point injection therapy.",
    "The relationship between myofascial trigger points and tactile hypoesthesia appears to be mediated through the primary somatosensory cortex."
  ]
